"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-03-18-dame-laura-kenny-retires-cycling-ahead-olympics-20482045\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"DameLaura Kenny, Britain's most successful female Olympic athlete, has announced her retirement ahead of this summer'sOlympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 24, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9749978072256281, \"rank\": 0.02518387044815112, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 31-year-oldwon five Olympic gold medalsduring her cycling career and was expected to compete at this year's Games inParis.\", \"from\": 129, \"to\": 255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I always knew deep down I would know when was the right time,' Kenny toldBBCBreakfast.\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have had an absolute blast but now is the time for me to hang that bike up.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 424, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kenny and her husband, Sir Jason Kenny- Britain's most decorated Olympian - last year welcomed a second son to their family and she said spending time at home played a key role in her decision.\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9749978072256281, \"rank\": 0.02518387044815112, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 491, \"end\": 499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999907172426652, \"rank\": 8.891348729638626e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's been in my head a little while, the sacrifices of leaving the children and your family at home is really quite big and it really is a big decision to make,' Kenny said.\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 795, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sorry, this video is not available any more.\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'More and more, I was struggling to do that.\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 887, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"More people asking me what races was I doing, what training camps was I going on - I did not want to go ultimately and that's what it came down to.\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I knew the minute I was getting those feelings.\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1085, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Once I said to Jase, 'I do not think I want to ride a bike anymore', I started to feel relief.'\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kenny also said she was no longer motivated to add more Olympic medals to her stellar career on the track.\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was getting these hesitant feelings,' she said.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1341, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Going on to win another gold medal, as much as I would love to do that, it wasn't giving me the energy I wanted anymore, it just wasn't.\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I wasn't thinking, 'I really want to go on and win one'.\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1539, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was thinking, 'I really want to stay at home with the children'.'\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1607, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1657, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1729, \"entities\": []}, {\"se